data.description: Welcome to the newest phase in Olde Town Village! Perfect for families of all sizes is the Hayden plan. A 5 bedroom, 3 bath and 2 car garage home. As you enter through the foyer, you will find a large open living space joined by a gorgeous dining and kitchen area with Whirlpool stainless steel appliances. Bedroom 1 is located on the second floor of the home and features a bath with a garden tub, separate shower, dual vanity sinks and large walk in closet. Standard features of this home also include; vinyl flooring throughout, carpet on the stairs, hallways, bedrooms, laminate countertops, and traditional 8' ceilings
